<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id6c18f94e-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e" identifier="/us/usc/t33/s1522"><num value="1522">§ 1522.</num><heading> Limitations on export provisions of <ref href="/us/usc/t30/s185/u">section 185(u) of title 30</ref> unaffected</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this chapter shall be construed to amend, restrict, or otherwise limit the application of <ref href="/us/usc/t30/s185/u">section 185(u) of title 30</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id6c18f94f-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e">(<ref href="/us/pl/93/627/s23">Pub. L. 93–627, § 23</ref>, <date date="1975-01-03">Jan. 3, 1975</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/88/2147">88 Stat. 2147</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
